name: Portraits from the Multiverse - The 57 Club - Janis
description:
Portraits from the Multiverse is a series of AI-generated works that imagine alternate realities where things are not quite what they are now. The 57 Club shows what the recording and visual artists in The 27 Club would look like if they lived to be 57 years old. 

You can read about how I created the series here, https://robgon.medium.com/list/portraits-from-the-multiverse-583b06d2130e
